  "prompt": "I am going to organising an party, for that I need to clean my home on or before 31/12/2017. So suggest me cleaning service company in Perth?",
  "response": "If you're looking for reliable cleaning services in Perth to get your home ready for a party by **31st December 2017**, here are some reputable cleaning companies you can consider:\n\n### 1. **Absolute Domestics**  \n   - Known for thorough home cleaning services.  \n   - Offers one-off or regular cleaning.  \n   - Website: [Absolute Domestics](https://www.absolutedomestics.com.au)  \n\n### 2. **Jim's Cleaning**  \n   - A trusted brand with professional cleaners.  \n   - Specializes in deep cleaning, spring cleaning, and party preparation.  \n   - Website: [Jim's Cleaning](https://www.jimscleaning.com.au)  \n\n### 3. **Perfect House Cleaning Perth**  \n   - Provides eco-friendly cleaning services.  \n   - Customizable packages for one-off cleans or event preparations.  \n   - Website: [Perfect House Cleaning Perth](https://www.perfecthousecleaningperth.com.au)  \n\n### 4. **Urban You**  \n   - Offers flexible booking and professional cleaning services.  \n   - Great for last-minute cleaning needs.  \n   - Website: [Urban You](https://www.urbanyou.com.au)  \n\n### 5. **Cleaning Exec**  \n   - Specializes in one-off cleans and post-party cleaning.  \n   - High-quality service with experienced cleaners.  \n   - Website: [Cleaning Exec](https://www.cleaningexec.com.au)  \n\n### Tips:  \n- Book as early as possible, as December is a busy time for cleaning companies.  \n- Clearly communicate your requirements, including the deadline (31/12/2017).  \n- Check reviews and ask for quotes to compare services.  \n\nGood luck with your party preparations! \ud83c\udf89",
